Added a `PduOutletStatus` model that stores the last-polled on/off state of each PDU outlet, with full UI and REST API.
Added a "PDU Status" tab to the device detail page that lists each outlet's stored state as a green (On) / red (Off) badge.
Added per-row On/Off/Reboot buttons to the PDU outlet status view that enqueue the matching power action for that outlet (Power Off Protection still enforced).
Extended the Status job to persist outlet state to `PduOutletStatus`, and to refresh every PDU when run without a device so it can be scheduled on an interval.
